  * ~~iatiregistry.org~~

 * ~~s052.okserver.org~~
  * ~~datacatalogs.org~~

 * ~~s004.okserver.org / eu4.okfn.org / solr.okfn.org~~
  * thedatahub.org (=www.ckan.net)
  * datagm.org.uk
  * ~~publicdata.eu~~
  * hri.fi (dev.fvh.fi?)
  * it.ckan.net
  * ie.ckan.net
  * cz.ckan.net
  * register.data.overheid.nl (nl.ckan.net?)
  * no.ckan.net / datakilder.no
  * br.ckan.net
  * colorado.ckan.net
  * at.ckan.net


